            <title>0.1.4</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2026 10:41:28 -0700</pubDate>
            <link>https://krehin.com/</link>
            <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.1.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[- Krehin now opens straight into a new draft, so you can start writing right away.
- The filter sidebar and post list tuck away for a clean, focused editor, and toggle back from the toolbar.
- The editor blends into the window instead of sitting on a hard black panel.
- A simpler, refreshed app icon.
]]></description>
